node.text: A lot of you might be wondering why we took the time to make this video, and to that we say *ahem* 🗣MIND YA BUSINESS!!! 🙄😤 We can feel you judging us! 😩 No this is not an ad, yes we took the time to do this, because it makes us happy, and we hope it makes you happy too. We’re literally trying to manifest this sauce into our lives lol. Don’t block our blessing! @BLovesLife2 We are ready when you are!!! 🍴😁👍🏿

node.title: People trying BLove’s Smackalicious Sauce for the First Time! 😍🤤😋😭

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EBC on July 29, 2021 tagging @simonebiles. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'mobbdë3ń @Deen8 What does this woman have to prove to ANYONE?'.

node.text: We stand, split leap, wolf turn (on the beam), aerial with a connecting double layout, back handspring into the Biles II, Yurchenko double pike (which we obviously don’t stick because our immense, unearthly power caused us to over rotate) and front walkover, round off, back handspring into the Biles triple-double (which we again over rotate and fly out of bounds, due to having legs like bull and being strvongest voman in the vorld 💪🏿😏) with @SimoneBiles. ✊🏿💜

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by EBC on July 29, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of 2 people and text that says 'Tressie McMillan Cottom @tressiemcphd If I'm the best in the whole cotdamn world and you won't say it with your whole chest because of feelings, also going home and letting you have your little asterisk ass games by yourself. am Tressie McMillan Cottom @tressiemcphd TAKE YOUR BALL AND GO HOME, SIMONE'.

Photo by EBC on July 29, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Tressie McMillan Cottom @tressiemcphd Anyway. afflicted by the guilt of their un- earned privilege. When we per- form some existential service to men, to capital, to political power, to white women, and even to other "people of color" who are marginally closer to white than they are to black, then we are superwomen.7 We are fulfilling our purpose in the natural order of things. When, instead, black women are strong in service of themselves, that same strength, wisdom, and wit become evi- dence of our incompetence.'.

node.text: 😭😭😭😭 It could all be so simple. And we feel like the issue was never with the request (because let’s be honest, it really wasn’t a big ask lol), but the issue was rather the HUUUGE overreaction to when the request wasn’t fulfilled. Like now now… we know you had a long day, but we forgot, just like *boops nose* you forgot. No need to threaten anyone’s lives. Ain’t nothing some warm water or a few minutes in the microwave can’t fix lol 🤷🏿‍♂️🤷🏾‍♀️😂. What do y’all think?

node.text: 🗣WE LOVE TO SEE BLACK WOMEN CHOOSING THEMSELVES!!! 😭😭😭🙌🏿🙌🏿🙌🏿 First @naomiosaka and now @simonebiles. The world loves to see Black women drive themselves into the ground, but these queens aren’t having it, and we have to stan. And @SimoneBiles you could’ve went out there and did the hokey pokey on the floor and we would STILL be calling you the GOAT because you earned that title looong before the Olympics. But the fact that you made this courageous decision not just for yourself, but also for your team, is just another testament to your beautiful spirit, and PROOF that the TRUE gold is in your hort 💛 (ew 🤢 sorry, that was gross, but y’all get it). WE LOVE YOU SIMONE!!! And we are forever proud ✊🏿😌💜 (Also @lesdogggg you need to be a sports commentator like yesterday 😭😂) #BlackMentalHealthMatters

node.text: 😭😭😂😩😂 We be goin thru it chile. And the fact that we all be doing and saying and going thru the same thing, makes it even funnier. Now don’t get it twisted, Black hair is actually one of the wonders of the world. But DOING it, will have you contemplating your whole existence lol. Oh well 🤷🏿‍♂️🤷🏾‍♀️. Time to go detangle 🙃 #IntoTheThickOfIt

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EBC on July 13, 2021 tagging @basketballasart. May be an image of 1 person and child.

Photo by EBC on July 12, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says '@maddiebckley who who is one character you believe was PERFECTLY cast? like the role was just made for that actor and nobody else could embody it they way they did?'.

node.text: **Warning::Language** 😍😌 There really is nothing quite like a perfect casting. It feels good to know that the movie was brought to life in the best way. Of course we wanted to add other people to this list, but we only begotten 10 slides 🤷🏿‍♂️🤷🏾‍♀️. So, comment which castings you think should be added to the list, and maybe we’ll make a part 2. 🙃😬👍🏿

node.text: ✊🏿🏄🏿‍♀️💜 Wow. 🥺🥲Black people, we can truly do it all.  To be honest, @nique_miller is the first Black girl surfer we’ve ever seen. But then we stumbled across @blackgirlssurf, and our horts are so full to see that there are so many Black Girl Surfers out there! Teach us, so we can be cool too 😩😅😂. @nique_miller 👏🏿👏🏿👏🏿💜
